{"article_id":"TZifOsjtJwhV6WN2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford ' s written testimony for Thursday ' s Senate hearing with Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh begins with a stunning , simple summary","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"of why she has come forward with an accusation of sexual assault against a man","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"who could soon be one of the most powerful people in the country .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"\" I am here today","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"not because I want to be .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"I am terrified , \"","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Ford writes in the testimony ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"which was posted online Wednesday afternoon .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"\" I am here","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"because I believe","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"it is my civic duty to tell you what happened to me","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"while Brett Kavanaugh and I were in high school . \"","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"She describes her childhood in Bethesda , Maryland , and the social scene","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"involving her all-girls alma mater Holton-Arms and Georgetown Prep , the all-boys school","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that Kavanaugh attended .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"\" This is how I met Brett Kavanaugh , the boy","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"who sexually assaulted me , \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Ford writes .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"She goes on to recount the day of the alleged assault ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"which Kavanaugh has repeatedly and unequivocally denied .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"( He has also denied accusations of sexual misconduct from two other women :","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Deborah Ramirez and Julie Swetnick . )","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Ford says","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"after swimming at Columbia Country Club ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"she went to a small gathering of friends at a house in the Washington area .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"She says","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"she had one beer while at the house","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"but that Kavanaugh and his friend Mark Judge were \" visibly drunk . \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Early in the evening , I went up a narrow set of stairs","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"leading from the living room to a second floor","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to use the bathroom .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"When I got to the top of the stairs ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"I was pushed from behind into a bedroom .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"I couldn ' t see","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"who pushed me .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Brett and Mark came into the bedroom","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and locked the door behind them .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"There was music already playing in the bedroom .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"It was turned up louder by either Brett or Mark","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"once we were in the room .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"I was pushed onto the bed","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and Brett got on top of me .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"He began running his hands over my body","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"and grinding his hips into me .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"I yelled ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"hoping","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"someone downstairs might hear me ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"and tried to get away from him ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"but his weight was heavy .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Brett groped me","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and tried to take off my clothes .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" I believed","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"he was going to rape me .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"I tried to yell for help .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"When I did ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Brett put his hand over my mouth","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"to stop me from screaming , \"","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"Ford says .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" This was what terrified me the most ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"and has had the most lasting impact on my life .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"It was hard for me to breathe ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and I thought","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"that Brett was accidentally going to kill me . \"","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Kavanaugh and Judge ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"according to Ford ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"\" were drunkenly laughing during the attack .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"They both seemed to be having a good time . \"","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Ford writes","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that at one point , Judge jumped on the bed ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Kavanaugh fell off her ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and she ran out of the room","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"and left the house .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"She also offered an explanation","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"for why she did not report the assault immediately to the police or her parents .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" I did not want to tell my parents","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that I , at age 15 , was in a house","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"without any parents present ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"drinking beer with boys , \"","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Ford says .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" I tried to convince myself","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"because Brett did not rape me ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"I should be able to move on","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and just pretend","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that it had never happened . \"","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"Ford then recounts what she shared with her husband and friends over the years about the attack , her struggle","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"to decide whether to come forward","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"once Kavanaugh ' s Supreme Court candidacy picked up steam ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and what her life has been like","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"since her story became public .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"She ends with another explanation","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"of why she has come forward .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"\" My motivation","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"in coming forward","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"was to provide the facts","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"about how Mr. Kavanaugh ' s actions have damaged my life ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"so that you can take that into serious consideration","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"as you make your decision","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"about how to proceed , \"","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Ford testifies .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"\" It is not my responsibility to determine whether Mr. Kavanaugh deserves to sit on the Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"My responsibility is to tell the truth . \"","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"In his own written testimony , Kavanaugh says","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"that","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"while he is \" not questioning","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"that Dr. Ford may have been sexually assaulted by some person in some place at some time , \"","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"he has \" never done that to her or to anyone .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"I am innocent of this charge . \"","depth":3},{"id":109,"text":"You can read Ford ' s full testimony on Document Cloud or below .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":218,"right":109,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":212,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":138,"right":211,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":112,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":0,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":130,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":